===Etymology 1===
From a root {{m|und|*ŋ(ˤ)rar||slope, nearly vertical side}}, whence also {{och-l|巘|hill|tr=*ŋ(r)ar(ʔ)}}, {{och-l|山|tr=*s-ŋrar|mountain}}, and {{och-l|顏|tr=*C.ŋˤrar|forehead}} ({{zh-ref|Baxter & Sagart, 2014}}).

Same word as {{zh-l|崖|cliff}} and {{zh-l|睚|rim (of the eye)}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

